{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/setup-latex-with-vscode-in-macos/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yitong's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5446ae8f-f9d2-5742-b418-b5457e82bf0a","excerpt":"Recently, I need to update my resume, which is written in Latex. Here is how I make it work on MacOS and VSCode. Install Latex compilers & libraries (You need…","html":"<p>Recently, I need to update my resume, which is written in Latex.</p>\n<p>Here is how I make it work on MacOS and VSCode.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install Latex compilers &#x26; libraries</li>\n</ul>\n<p>(You need <code>brew</code> for this. If you haven’t install it, follow the instruction in <a href=\"https://brew.sh/\">here</a> )</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># We will use VSCode as editor, so `-no-gui` part comes.</span>\nbrew cask <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mactex-no-gui\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Update all Latex libraries</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> tlmgr update --self\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> tlmgr update --all\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># (Optional) Update all TeX format.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># You will need this for Chinese support library - CTEX</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> fmtutil-sys --all</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Install <code>LaTeX Workshop</code> extension in VSCode</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So far, if you don’t need Chinese support, you are all set and good to go.</p>\n<p>However, if you do, there are a few more steps to do.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Setup <code>LaTeX Workshop</code></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">// .vscode/setting.json</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"latex-workshop.latex.tools\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xelatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xelatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"args\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-synctex=1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-interaction=nonstopmode\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-file-line-error\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-pdf\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"%DOC%\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"latexmk\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"latexmk\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"args\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-synctex=1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-interaction=nonstopmode\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-file-line-error\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-pdf\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"%DOC%\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"args\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-synctex=1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-interaction=nonstopmode\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"-file-line-error\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"%DOC%\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bibtex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bibtex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"args\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%DOCFILE%\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"latex-workshop.latex.recipes\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xelatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"tools\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"xelatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex -> bibtex -> pdflatex*2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"tools\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bibtex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pdflatex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>In your <code>.tex</code> file, add these lines in the top</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tex\"><pre class=\"language-tex\"><code class=\"language-tex\"><span class=\"token function selector\">\\documentclass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">% Starts from here</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">% import the Chinese support library</span>\n<span class=\"token function selector\">\\usepackage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">xeCJK</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">% set font for your document.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">% You can find all the fonts in mac's `Font Book`</span>\n<span class=\"token function selector\">\\setCJKmainfont</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>STSong<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Now, you can have a happy time coding Latex in VSCode! Enjoy!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Setup Latex with VSCode in MacOS","date":"November 17, 2019","description":"Simple steps to setup Latex with VSCode in MacOS"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/setup-latex-with-vscode-in-macos/","previous":null,"next":null}}}